  "comment": "One who is looking for very powerful beam moving heads, is looking for the BSL Impact Beam 7R. This moving head is very well suited for outdoor use because of the use of the Osram 7R gas-discharge lamp. The lamp has a beam angle of just 1,3 degrees, which makes that all the power is projected in a narrow beam. As a result, you get powerful beams which are intense, even from a distance. Furthermore, the moving head is equipped with RDM functionality. This way you can not only remotely set the DMX address and mode, but read temperatures and lifetime of the lamp as well.",
